V 1.0-55 (2004-03-06)

* Added detection for Genius Vivid 1200 EX.
* Fixed product id of Mustek BearPaw 2448 TA Plus.
* Other minor updates.
 
V 1.0-54 (2004-02-10)

* Added basic support for Plustek OpticSlim 2400. Thanks to Radoslaw Grzanka and
