V 1.0-46 (2003-04-27)

- Added Genius 3x as working scanner, removed testing flag.
- Added Artec 2000 e+ to manpage.
- Added detection for the Plustek OpticPro U16B.

V 1.0-45 (2003-04-11)

- Updated Mustek BearPaw 1200 CU Plus white strip value.
